sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant budapp
    participant budsim
    participant budcluster

    Client->>budapp: POST /endpoints {model_id, cluster_id, config}
    budapp->>budapp: Validate request, create endpoint record
    budapp->>budsim: Request optimization config
    budsim-->>budapp: {tp, pp, batch_size, replicas}
    budapp->>budcluster: Deploy model with config
    budcluster-->>budapp: {workflow_id, status: DEPLOYING}
    budapp-->>Client: {endpoint_id, status: DEPLOYING}
